">original article</a>.</em></p></div><h3 class="alsoTaggedIn">Also tagged with</h3><br><ul class="c-header__tags c-tags c-tags--left"><li class="c-tags__tag"><a class="c-tags__link" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Tags" data-event-label="Nayib Bukele" data-event-non-interaction="false"  href="/topic/nayib-bukele">Nayib Bukele</a></li><li class="c-tags__tag"><a class="c-tags__link" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Tags" data-event-label="legal tender" data-event-non-interaction="false"  href="/topic/legal-tender">legal tender</a></li><li class="c-tags__tag"><a class="c-tags__link" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Tags" data-event-label="El Salvador’s economy." data-event-non-interaction="false"  href="/topic/el-salvadors-economy">El Salvador’s economy.</a></li><li class="c-tags__tag"><a class="c-tags__link" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Tags" data-event-label="El Salvador" data-event-non-interaction="false"  href="/topic/el-salvador">El Salvador</a></li></ul><footer class="c-article__pubDate" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;"><div>
